<h1 style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 25px 0; line-height: 1.3;">Welcome to CrediScore!</h1>

<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #666; margin: 0 0 30px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
    Dear <strong style="color: #2C5270;"><%= name %></strong>,
</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 25px 0;">
    Congratulations! Your account has been successfully created. We're excited to have you join the CrediScore community where businesses and customers connect with trust and transparency.
</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 25px 0;">
    CrediScore helps you discover verified businesses, share authentic reviews, and build a trusted ecosystem for commerce.
</p>

<!-- Features Section -->
<div style="background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h3 style="color: #2C5270; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 15px 0;">What you can do with CrediScore:</h3>
  <ul style="color: #555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Discover Trusted Businesses:</strong> Find verified businesses in your area</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Share Authentic Reviews:</strong> Help others by sharing your experiences</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Build Your Reputation:</strong> Establish yourself as a trusted reviewer</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;"><strong>Stay Informed:</strong> Get updates on businesses you follow</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- CTA Section -->
<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <% if (verificationUrl) { %>
    <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" 
       style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5270 0%, #3A6B8A 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 35px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(44, 82, 112, 0.3);">
      Verify Your Email →
    </a>
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; margin: 15px 0 0 0;">
      Verification link expires at: <strong><%= new Date(Date.now() + 86400000).toLocaleString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: '2-digit', day: '2-digit', hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' }) %></strong>
    </p>
  <% } else { %>
    <a href="<%= appUrl %>/dashboard" 
       style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C5270 0%, #3A6B8A 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 35px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(44, 82, 112, 0.3);">
      Go to Dashboard →
    </a>
  <% } %>
</div>

<!-- Support Section -->
<div style="background: #f0f8ff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
  <h3 style="color: #2C5270; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Need Help Getting Started?</h3>
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 15px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
    Our support team is here to help you make the most of your CrediScore experience.
  </p>
  <a href="mailto:support@crediscore.com" 
     style="color: #2C5270; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px;">
    Contact Support →
  </a>
</div>

<!-- Closing Message -->
<p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 1.8; margin: 30px 0 20px 0;">
  We're thrilled to have you join the CrediScore community. Let's work together to build trust and transparency in business!
</p>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #666; margin: 0; line-height: 1.6;">
  Best regards,<br>
  <strong style="color: #2C5270;">The CrediScore Team</strong>
</p>